PrecisSetting apart, for the use and benefit of the PELICAN LAKE BAND, of land situated in the Rural Municipality of Spiritwood No. 496, Province of Saskatchewan, mines and minerals included, as follows: 128 hectares as an addition to Pelican Lake Indian Reserve No. 191-B, and another 27 hectares as an addition to their Reserve No. 191-C.
